Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.66,0:10:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 10 9 8 7！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.36,0:10:17.87,Other4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs34\pos(648,306)\bord0}报名完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.83,0:10:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.44,0:10:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空太
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.05,0:10:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.48,0:10:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.60,0:10:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七海好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.99,0:10:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青山
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.28,0:10:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么什么？ 真白 小七怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.96,0:10:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青山
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.19,0:10:47.00,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小七
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.53,0:10:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 青山 你还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.45,0:10:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青山你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.01,0:10:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去 今天一定要去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.64,0:11:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 让我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.35,0:11:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏偏是这个时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.36,0:11:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然早就知道会她会累垮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.39,0:11:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,育成班的发表会是今天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.27,0:11:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她应该是怕被我们看到才准备提早出发的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.84,0:11:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她自己是肯定会去的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.38,0:11:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但总不能让她去吧 虽然很可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.99,0:11:26.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.39,0:11:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的话会去的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.85,0:11:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是我的话 会去的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.04,0:11:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 椎名…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.18,0:11:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七海想去的话 就让她去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.05,0:11:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她去吧 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.34,0:11:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七海她很努力 每天都忙到很晚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.49,0:11:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这我当然知道 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.51,0:11:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.09,0:11:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椎名…？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.06,0:12:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢来就好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.36,0:12:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 你们从刚才开始就在闹些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.57,0:12:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青山？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.74,0:12:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.58,0:12:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.92,0:12:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.73,0:12:31.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都烧成这样了 还打算出去？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.77,0:12:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去休息
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.04,0:12:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.21,0:12:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会听取你的意见 给我回房间…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.49,0:12:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的士来了 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.32,0:12:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主我就收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.46,0:12:45.78,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 给我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.42,0:12:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空太 之后就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.84,0:12:48.76,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三鹰 你干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.41,0:12:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.77,0:12:50.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小七坐上去 学弟也快点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.77,0:12:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.59,0:12:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 椎名
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.24,0:12:52.59,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快上快上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.26,0:12:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 那么前进吧的士 GOGO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.58,0:13:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可连英语也用上了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.31,0:12:59.10,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三鹰 别趁乱摸我的胸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.10,0:13:00.94,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为胸在那里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.94,0:13:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说得和山一样！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.94,0:13:02.45,NETA,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注：此处NETA出自马洛里的“因为山在那里”
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.69,0:13:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青山 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.72,0:13:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 之后我自己能走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.50,0:13:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束的时候我还会在这等你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.13,0:13:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青山 我在找你呢 快点来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.99,0:13:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.68,0:13:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去咖啡厅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.57,0:13:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就呆在这
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.82,0:13:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要等很久的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.92,0:13:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.09,0:13:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.80,0:13:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七海太累了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.29,0:13:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.33,0:13:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.79,0:13:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧 她肯定会生气的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.49,0:14:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.22,0:14:09.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是突然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.01,0:14:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,买把伞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.04,0:14:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.05,0:14:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我们一起去买吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.66,0:14:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 慌忙之中把今天的事给忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.68,0:14:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.60,0:14:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.37,0:14:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会纠结于发售日
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.38,0:14:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.80,0:14:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.64,0:14:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内容我都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.70,0:14:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是… 你不开心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.50,0:14:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.51,0:15:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.40,0:15:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还在下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.36,0:15:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冲到车站去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.43,0:15:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.97,0:15:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青山
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.64,0:15:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 七海 你知道因为你的错给大家添了多少麻烦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.99,0:15:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.81,0:15:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知如此还不如请假呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.37,0:15:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.28,0:15:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.07,0:15:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你们添麻烦了 真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.40,0:15:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.07,0:15:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都没做成 好不容易把我带过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.23,0:15:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了今天一直在准备
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.16,0:15:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而全部都付诸东流了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.83,0:16:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太差劲了 太没用了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.37,0:16:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.83,0:16:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能够
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.65,0:16:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神田君你也说过 不要勉强 不要乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.69,0:16:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擅自去背负很多东西 以为能更好地解决
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.76,0:16:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是却在逞强 我真是个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.66,0:16:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的 青山 无视我的话也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.16,0:16:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说这种话啊 骂我是笨蛋 蠢货啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.30,0:16:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然 不然的话我会…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.74,0:16:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么说自己啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.25,0:16:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青山要是笨蛋的话 全世界都是笨蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.09,0:16:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么啊 你才别跟我开玩笑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.51,0:16:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神田君…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.03,0:16:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青山已经很努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.02,0:16:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们非常清楚这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.12,0:16:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 为什么要说这种话…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.68,0:16:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说的话 我会…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.37,0:17:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我一直在期待有人对我说这句话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.22,0:17:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小七一直在硬撑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.13,0:17:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不管对待他人还是自己都很严格嘛 不过这只是一直以来的习惯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.74,0:17:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我终于明白仁学长所说的 印象不同的意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.72,0:17:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青山在与某些东西作斗争 例如父母的反对和自己本身
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.54,0:17:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许是不想依靠任何人 只要撒娇了一次就会有下一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.04,0:17:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能硬着头皮把自己逼向绝路
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.85,0:17:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能理解这些对她来说也算是一种救赎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.20,0:17:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白还在看着青山吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.85,0:17:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 她似乎想了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.46,0:18:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.64,0:18:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.80,0:18:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.26,0:18:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,参鸡汤 我觉得这种时候做些特别点的火锅比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.74,0:18:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.96,0:18:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为小七让我们看到了她的弱点嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.94,0:18:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弱点…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.26,0:18:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说参鸡汤可不是火锅啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.47,0:18:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太在意细节可是会降低受欢迎度的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.35,0:18:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虎次郎 我该怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.23,0:18:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.08,0:18:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 昨天那样也太丢脸了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.13,0:18:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭丧的脸又被看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.32,0:18:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是发烧 可一直被他抱着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.64,0:18:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还趁乱把人家紧紧抱住了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.63,0:19:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又不是故意的！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.95,0:19:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说些有的没的 赶紧推倒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.40,0:19:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虎次郎你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.16,0:19:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是虎次郎吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.51,0:19:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你敲门啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.90,0:19:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敲了 而且门又是开的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.83,0:19:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.15,0:19:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到抱枕还会有说话的功能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.94,0:19:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要和别人说…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.75,0:19:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟透了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.36,0:19:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.99,0:19:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.96,0:19:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.65,0:19:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁热吃 不然会凉掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.58,0:19:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.03,0:19:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去感谢仁学长吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.24,0:19:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.56,0:20:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像一整晚都在握着我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.12,0:20:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她好像认为自己也有责任
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.50,0:20:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.87,0:20:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且最理解青山的人就是椎名了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.26,0:20:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不是因为椎名 我就阻止你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.21,0:20:20.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过她说 如果是自己的话就会去 所以带她去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.58,0:20:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,低头拜托了大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.78,0:20:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一直看着青山的努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.56,0:20:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.49,0:20:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没去的话 我肯定会后悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.58,0:20:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.34,0:20:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着椎名同学 就觉得自己还远远不足
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.10,0:20:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天画漫画都画到很晚 无数次地重画
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.36,0:20:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本以为有才能的人是不会努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.90,0:20:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要追上才能 该怎么做才好呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.18,0:20:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追上…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.21,0:20:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准盯着看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.13,0:21:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能看椎名同学的睡脸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.24,0:21:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的房间也不准看 也不准看我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.35,0:21:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要我怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.57,0:21:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 别靠得太近
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.41,0:21:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫名地伤人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.63,0:21:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为人家还没洗澡…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.79,0:21:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说参鸡汤很好喝！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.58,0:21:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 椎名同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.39,0:21:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七海你没事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.68,0:21:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了椎名同学呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.76,0:21:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神田君 关于“真白值日”
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.82,0:21:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 说实话我没法继续下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.96,0:21:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我实在是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.06,0:21:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.11,0:21:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你能依靠我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.69,0:21:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道谢的人应该是我才对
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.66,0:21:43.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 椎名同学
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.07,0:21:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.71,0:21:47.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要七海叫我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.43,0:21:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 真白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.44,0:21:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.99,0:21:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下 椎…真白
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.55,0:22:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神田君 快想想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.05,0:22:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是负责真白的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.78,0:22:09.54,Other4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(628,186)}『真白值日』的工作由青山七海交还给了神田空太
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.78,0:22:09.54,Other4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(946,312)}记录·神田空太
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.78,0:22:09.54,Other4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(514,542)}神田君 非常抱歉 忘了说一件事 于是就写在着了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.78,0:22:09.54,Other4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(450,586)}如果对真白做奇怪的事我绝对不会放过你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.78,0:22:09.54,Other4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1008,680)}追加·青山七海
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.31,0:22:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个情况已经是不可能的了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.80,0:22:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管用什么手段都没用
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.62,0:22:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快起来 真白 真白！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.08,0:23:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空太
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.40,0:23:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我吹头发
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.35,0:23:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你出道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.55,0:23:49.80,Title01,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\3c&H31B1ED&\pos(650,446)\blur2}#07 女孩的协约
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.39,0:23:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优子要来了 优子要来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.66,0:02:23.85,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}一回目　殴れて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.97,0:02:27.23,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}二回目って　どうだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.57,0:02:34.56,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}偶然じゃないよね　三回目が遭うのは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.08,0:02:37.99,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}変わった人だと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.26,0:02:41.51,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}割と皆いうけど
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.01,0:02:48.77,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}気になったことは 違うんだ　そこじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.32,0:02:55.39,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}君は多分純粋で　純粋を負けず
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.56,0:03:02.67,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}だから小さな日常にさえ　立ち向かって
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.69,0:03:09.83,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}夢を持ってきた言葉じゃ　足りない夢にありが
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.83,0:03:13.38,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}きっとこんな風に始まる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.38,0:03:16.93,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}新しいトキメキ世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:24.04,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}夢を持ってきた言葉を　知らないふりして行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.07,0:03:28.12,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}トキメキと夢のありか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.66,0:02:23.85,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}第一回 被人殴打
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.97,0:02:27.23,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}第二回又会如何呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.57,0:02:34.56,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}会有第三回绝对不是偶然吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.08,0:02:37.99,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}真是个怪人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.26,0:02:41.51,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}大家好像都这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.01,0:02:48.77,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}应该在意的事不是那个啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.32,0:02:55.39,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}你或许非常单纯 并且不向单纯低头
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.56,0:03:02.67,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}所以即便是简单的日常也会抵抗到底
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.69,0:03:09.83,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}充满着梦想的话语便是梦想不足的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.83,0:03:13.38,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}一定是像这样开始的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.38,0:03:16.93,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}那片崭新的心跳世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:24.04,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}充满着梦想的话语 就当作没有听过继续前行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.07,0:03:28.12,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}走向那心跳与梦的所在
