Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.88,0:22:15.13,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}過ぎるだけの時間じゃ付与する
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.85,0:22:24.18,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}刻まなくちゃ　ここに居ると心が叫ぶ瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.59,0:22:26.66,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}I am dreaming
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.97,0:22:29.84,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}迷いながら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.84,0:22:33.37,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}涙をのみこんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.99,0:22:35.98,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}不器用だね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.40,0:22:39.66,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}夢も遠回り
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.00,0:22:45.65,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}大空を見上げ何も言えず
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.99,0:22:53.95,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}胸が痛む訳考えていた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.17,0:22:55.61,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}DAYS of DASH
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.61,0:22:58.47,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}風を走り抜けて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.47,0:23:04.86,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}君と僕の仲で何が始まったのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.86,0:23:06.95,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}分からないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.97,0:23:14.55,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}キメキラ光る太陽が照らす場所をずっと進もう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.68,0:23:20.22,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}永遠など　知らないけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.88,0:22:15.13,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}给予了我所度过的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.85,0:22:24.18,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}必须在这里刻下心灵吼叫的那一瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.59,0:22:26.66,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}I am dreaming
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.97,0:22:29.84,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}一直很迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.84,0:22:33.37,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}强忍着泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.99,0:22:35.98,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}真是不中用
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.40,0:22:39.66,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}连梦想也与我无缘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.00,0:22:45.65,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}看着天空一句话也说不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.99,0:22:53.95,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}一直思考着胸口的那股痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.17,0:22:55.61,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}DAYS of DASH
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.61,0:22:58.47,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}追赶着清风
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.47,0:23:04.86,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}你与我之间发生了什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.86,0:23:06.95,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}虽然不是很明白
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.97,0:23:14.55,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}向着那耀眼的太阳所照耀之处前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.68,0:23:20.22,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}{\bord2}{\blur3}{\be1}永远什么的 我才不知道呢
